questiondata.strat-other: I was trying to imagine all the words in one of my rooms in the house (if it even makes sense). For example the words queen, brother, friend. I imagined them all sitting on the couch in my living room and every time the word was given i was trying to add this new word to the picture. For example, rug under their feet, shelf above their head and casket on top of it, snake on one brother's neck, etc.
